data.description: Your opportunity to take a popular Enclave floor plan to a new level at an attractive price. This front-loaded pool home has mountain view, 28 leased solar panels, and located away from traffic noise. Plenty of lounging area around the pool and spa will make your Palm Springs home a place to relax and live your best life. This floor plan allows for nice separation between the bedrooms and the attached casita/ 4th bedroom. This plan includes the optional 5th bedroom or sitting room. High ceilings and large windows and doors make for a light and bright home with indoor/outdoor living. When you enter the front door, the living room with fireplace gives a warm welcome. Entertain around the kitchen's center island while you prepare meals and cocktails. Feel like having a special dinner party? The dining area has just the right amount of space. The primary suite is very spacious with an attached sitting area, large walk-in closet, separate vanities, and large sliders doors leading to the pool area. There is plenty of space between bedrooms and there is also a half bath for guests. The attached casita has pool access, bathroom, and separate from the other bedrooms. If you want some privacy or quiet oasis, there is a covered patio with built in BBQ and sitting area with fountain. Nice sized pantry, laundry room, and two-car garage complete the home.
